17void to_byte(unsigned char *out, unsigned long long in, uint32_t bytes)
18{
19 int32_t i;
20 for (i = bytes-1; i >= 0; i--) {
21 out[i] = in & 0xff;
22 in = in >> 8;
23 }
24}
25
26void hexdump(const unsigned char *a, size_t len)
27{
28 size_t i;
29 for (i = 0; i < len; i++)
30 printf("%02x", a[i]);
31}
